race.description: The Breaking Point Challenge For The Cure Hcp
race.comment: Former NSW galloper AGED CARE (1) just ran into one better first-up for the new yard and should find this easier than what he faced down south. Has to be included in calculations. RICH AGAIN (2) has hit the top-four at his past six outings and is racing very consistently of late. Top claims. SINGULAR (2) won at Mackay two back and now drops back to the 1000m scamper. Consistent and warrants thought. STATESWOMAN (12) has placed three of five around this circuit and may earn some minor money. KEEP ON RUNNING (6) best of the rest. Has placed in his past two outings at this course and Bowen over longer distances.
